These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, fuchsia
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, librarian
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, trance
House: farmhouse, townhouse
1. the person driving the bike is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
3. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the fan of trance##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Color      | fuchsia      | apricot |
| Job          | librarian      | doctor       |
| Transport         | snowmobile | bike  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | satire      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | trance      |
| House         | townhouse    | farmhouse       |

