.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, teacher
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red
1. the nurse is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
2. the teacher is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the nurse is not to the left of the person who growsorchid##8
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Sport          | golf | skateboarding |
| Movie-Genre         | satire  | martial-arts  |
| Job           | nurse      | teacher  |
| Flower   | orchid     | azalea      |
| Pet           | ferret     | mouse    |
| Color     | light-blue  | blood-red     |

